cache.pool.app.label: cache.stash.driver.BlackHole.notes
Application: The Null driver will always take values but never saves them.

cache.pool.app.label: cache.stash.driver.Composite.notes
Application: The Composite driver acts as a wrapper around one or more drivers, allowing different drivers to work together in a single cache.

cache.pool.app.label: cache.stash.driver.Ephemeral.notes
Application: The Ephemeral driver stores data for the lifetime of the running process or web request.

cache.pool.app.label: cache.stash.driver.FileSystem.notes
Application: The File System driver stores values in files as native PHP code.

cache.pool.app.label: cache.stash.driver.support.notes
Application: Cache statistics are only available for the APC driver.
